        <Parent_String>farmland [300008632], agricultural land [300008631], cultural landscapes by function [300132441], cultural landscapes [300008932], landscapes (environments) [300008626], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
